  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA369-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu paṭṭapiṉṟai varaiyātu poruḷvayiṉ pirintu (ET: pirintuḻi) āṟṟāḷākiya talaimakaḷ vaṉpoṟai (ER, EV: vaṉpuṟai) yetiraḻintatu (G1+2: etirmoḻintatu).</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how SHE was desolate in the face of encouragement, being unable to bear it [when HE] separated for the sake of wealth without marrying after it had happened.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA369">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            cuṭarciṉan taṇintu kuṉṟañ cēra</l>
<l>            niṟaipaṟai kurukiṉam vicumpukan toḻuka</l>
<l>            vellai paipayak kaḻippi mullai</l>
<l>            yarumpuvā yaviḻum perumpuṉ mālai</l>
<l>            yiṉṟu malarva tāyi ṉaṉṟu</l>
<l>            maṟiyēṉ vāḻi tōḻi yaṟiyēṉ</l>
<l>            ñemaiyōṅ kuyarvarai yimaiyat tucci</l>
<l>            vāṉi ṉiḻitarum vayaṅkuveḷ ḷaruvi</l>
<l>            kaṅkaiyam pēryāṟṟuk karaiyiṟan tiḻitaruñ</l>
<l>            ciṟaiyaṭuṅ kaṭumpuṉa laṉṉave</l>
<l>            ṉiṟaiyaruṅ kāma nīntu māṟē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l rend="indent">If it blossoms even today, great bleak evening,</l>
<l rend="indent2">	when the bud mouths of the jasmine open, daylight passing gently,</l>
<l rend="indent2">	while a group of full-winged herons ascend the sky [and] pass,</l>
<l rend="indent2">	while the glow’s anger decreases [and] joins the hills,</l>
<l>I don’t know well, oh friend,</l>
<l rend="indent4">	I don’t know</l>
<l rend="indent">	a way of swimming the difficult desire that fills me,</l>
<l rend="indent2">	as the quick flood that breaks the banks,</l>
<l rend="indent3">	when the glowing white waterfall that descends from the sky,</l>
<l rend="indent4">	the Himālaya’s summit, [its] lofty mountains high with Ñemai trees,</l>
<l rend="indent3">	descends, traversing the shores of the big Gangā river.</l>
      </lg>
      </div>
